works.complaint:
The blog has been purposely created to defame our  
organization. This could have been done by our competitors to harm our  
businesses and clients. This, we think, is a misuse of the freedom offered
 
by the Internet and the third party is allegedly using the property of  
Google for doing so.

We are appealing to you to take action by informing the third party to  
remove/update their content and a failure would be considered as
deliberate  
attempt to defame us. In that case, we would request Google to take  
appropriate steps by removing the defaming content.
